                                "stop": 8.004,
                                "byte_start": 92753,
                                "byte_stop": 124831,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 99-1613, Shaw against Murphy will be announced by Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.004,
                        "stop": 140.121,
                        "byte_start": 124831,
